Video: PK

data.title: EVAN GEISELMAN: TRIPLE CROWN ROOKIE OF THE YEAR
data.description:
Big shout out to Evan Geiselman for taking home the Vans Triple Crown of Surfing Rookie of the Year Title. His first North Shore campaign sure was a good one -- a quarterfinal finish at Haleiwa and a top 32 finish out of a 128-man field at the Sunset Pro. Well done, EG!! 
Video: Tom Aiello

data.title: BALI PROJECT: WAVES FOR WATER AND H2O
data.description: Bali has given us surfers the waves of our lives. So why not give back? Jon Rose, Waves for Water and H2O need your help to bring clean drinking water to the thousands of Balinese who need it. Through the Clean Water Courier program you can make a difference by bringing a few water filters to Indonesia (or anywhere else in the world for that matter) and passing them out to the local communities. You're still able to do what you love (surf), and help in the process.
